episodes.title: Is Bonita Gardens a Cult?
episodes.description:
Bonita Gardens, a South Dallas apartment complex led by Mama Shirley has recently gone viral on TikTok and making headlines. The complex has people talking debating whether or not this is a cult.

In this video, Parke Jones breaks down how Bonita Gardens has become a social media phenomena, stories of the tenants and why it is the most controversial apartment complex in America!

00:00 The Leasing Office & Tenants
06:03 Bonita Gardens is in the Trenches
10:07 Who is Mama Shirley?

episodes.title: Cult Leader David Taylor Arrested for Human Trafficking
episodes.description:
Apostle David E Taylor has been arrested on shocking federal charges of forced labor, conspiracy and money laundering. Once celebrated for his ministry and massive following, Taylor is now accused of running his church like a cult. 

Be sure to subscribe to Parke Jones for more true crime stories.
